general-info.name: Name |
general-info.paragraph1: Ever since I was a kid I have always had an interest in technology. My greatest passion aside from playing with friends was using the family PC. When I was 14 I went to a job fair my school and it was there that I knew I want to be a software developer. Aside from picking IT classes all throughout highschool I selftaught myself some C++ using YouTube tutorials.
general-info.paragraph2: My hobbies include gaming, reading, DnD and graphic design. I used to sell my designs on fiverr to gain some petty cash during highschool.
